      <part part_index="1" name="A smart shopping cart" page="0" source="2">
      	<article allWordsNum="99">
            	<![CDATA[
Attention, please! I have good news for you. Your shopping time may be cut in half thanks to these new smart shopping carts (智能购物车).
What's so great about the carts? They are equipped with tablet computers (平板电脑). They can not only offer you coupons (优惠券), but also help you manage your shopping lists and find the products you need. What's more, you don't need to wait at the checkout stand. You can pay for your items simply through the tablets on the carts!
The biggest problem for you is to figure out what to do with all the extra time you have!
         	]]>
            </article>
